<s> Ok, there are two issues.  </s>
<s> First is that our default compiler is gcc, and, as has previously been reported, it doesn't like being called as cc -E without a *.c file on the command line.  </s>
<s> Sam posted a patch to fix this for real, I've just been saying: sed -e 's/CPP.*/CPP  </s>
<s> = cpp/' Options.orig  Options after running the configure script.  </s>
